<p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;text-indent: 2em">宝剑锋从磨砺出，梅花香自苦寒来。江西软件职业技术大学2023届毕业生在全国硕士研究生考试中不负众望，捷报频传。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;text-indent: 2em">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-05-29%2017%3A31%3A468853d88254a9dea7fde53ecebe08e68.jpg?Expires=2000712706&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=4PUITGGk2G6kI9gUu8e233tnkho%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;text-indent: 2em">据统计，我校52名同学分别被上海海事大学、海南大学、西安工程大学、江西师范大学、东华理工大学、南昌航空大学等国内高校录取，3名同学被悉尼大学等国外高校录取。其中，网络工程学院熊子欣同学成功考取“双一流高校”——海南大学。学校考研工作取得良好成效。希望同学们以考研学子为榜样，勤奋学习、再续佳绩。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important">2023年考取硕士研究生学生名单</span></span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-02%2009%3A58%3A311685666992821.png?Expires=2001031111&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=S1gFi1FrFr2XuBXq0Zljyw%2BRzBE%3D" alt="" width="800" height="1058" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-02%2009%3A58%3A481685667185119.png?Expires=2001031128&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=nV%2BJ9kjqJji0cjV6H38z6%2FOdCvM%3D" alt="" width="800" height="1152" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-02%2009%3A59%3A301685667223428.png?Expires=2001031170&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=zuGKmb41yu0W9ASgmDUTXnBy7%2BE%3D" alt="" width="800" height="582" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">星光不负赶路人 时光不负有心人</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">凡心所向，素履以往</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">生如逆旅，一苇以航</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">站在成功的岛屿，</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">回望四年的朝暮。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">叹初心未负，梦想终成。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">此刻，不必为前方迷惘</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">只管放肆一场，为青春，为理想</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;text-align: center">让我们为他们的成功喝彩！</p><p><br/></p>